      "text": "고! 더 가볼게요!",
      "voice": "F4",
      "speed": 1.12,
      "bytes": 88128,
      "sha256": "26009e00ffdb145808da844e087c0424eac8626f8bba1b23f9442289df8cfe65"
    },
    {
      "file": "matgo-female-stop.wav",
      "text": "스톱! 여기까지예요!",
      "voice": "F4",
      "speed": 1.12,
      "bytes": 111326,
      "sha256": "b029ab133d478ecc8b2032e1eff5922456642741f26facad2804b9c1635fb239"
    },
    {
      "file": "matgo-female-win.wav",
      "text": "제가 이겼어요! 신난다!",
      "voice": "F4",
      "speed": 1.12,
      "bytes": 138938,
      "sha256": "fb3ea4f70861bf8c0a4ed6ea8247c78eecf177ac20c9159600e894551f6663a4"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-capture.wav",
      "text": "딱! 이건 내가 먹지!",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.16,
      "bytes": 107142,
      "sha256": "e18ccce2e386412fef35b72ed06649e8167dfae738edf9bd5fc9accd022d2ebe"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-bonus-two.wav",
      "text": "쌍피네! 약 오르지?",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.16,
      "bytes": 92650,
      "sha256": "9e805fde4cf3c691341e3aefe0c6d13e1e220c5dd12a2dfe113a4c28e3ea7ea4"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-bonus-three.wav",
      "text": "쓰리피다! 어때?",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.16,
      "bytes": 76026,
      "sha256": "80df170a1ed49f2983f97f9b47f762f1f1215154a4d166b7a85d8286e56462d4"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-ppeok.wav",
      "text": "뻑이네! 이것도 재미지!",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.14,
      "bytes": 129458,
      "sha256": "c039326800a1da5c902f8298a16327730a2347bade6257690a5688d10b58da79"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-sweep.wav",
      "text": "싹쓸이! 구경 잘했지?",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.16,
      "bytes": 117652,
      "sha256": "c0e5e4b77b6edf0f00cad967cf903b58d4650a538e6318f026164c056265927c"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-ppeok-capture.wav",
      "text": "싼 패! 내가 챙긴다!",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.16,
      "bytes": 116754,
      "sha256": "8058fff1471bc814d0e5cdb8ac9280e9f965dc660415509d0d5719dbe2e8a3a1"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-self-ppeok.wav",
      "text": "자뻑! 운까지 내 편이네!",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.16,
      "bytes": 133006,
      "sha256": "9b519602125e5dfaa41104a04c189bff89c04ce071857e0cb00e6fafa16520fa"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-score.wav",
      "text": "점수 났네! 따라와 봐!",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.16,
      "bytes": 111308,
      "sha256": "aff7086c3cd13ee2cf9834da1ec6b9d3ea2a9ddcdce010185ff731a05f6626ba"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-go.wav",
      "text": "고! 겁나면 빠져!",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.14,
      "bytes": 103482,
      "sha256": "0af230d59226edc934c5937386d1cfcdc2044da982ecb22d71a2f81b826e7ae5"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-stop.wav",
      "text": "스톱! 딱 여기까지!",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.14,
      "bytes": 110842,
      "sha256": "e9b52070faf20ead283b975ed375f3e1cb45466e880ca8006c8314dacfa2be93"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-b-win.wav",
      "text": "내가 이겼네! 다음 판도 콜?",
      "voice": "M4",
      "speed": 1.14,
      "bytes": 140858,
      "sha256": "258b427f40451807626112c72c1002e1cf517f2023943d2a41c94630acf7977f"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-capture.wav",
      "text": "좋군. 이 패는 내가 가져가겠네.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 191198,
      "sha256": "a925702e17e89720c73a1903ebc5afeda5199feb4d039d43d87d4d6b8de16171"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-bonus-two.wav",
      "text": "쌍피로군. 운이 따르는군.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 168642,
      "sha256": "35fbe80a1251337536ba7bf8b22553081bd83c4eb9f7042e4ce7c94888a54562"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-bonus-three.wav",
      "text": "쓰리피라, 제법이군.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 105610,
      "sha256": "b7b2052decb854ee13bdcfdd72d295b43dc8cfcd2b2446f938c7dc44a79b8be1"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-ppeok.wav",
      "text": "허허, 뻑이로군.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 88610,
      "sha256": "921a8946d99e4e35f36a62f0deaf7eaba95d6904b1e5bd5b2da9e4098b4be857"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-sweep.wav",
      "text": "싹쓸이군. 패가 잘 붙는군.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 194648,
      "sha256": "81e994347c1b6ba98527966d7d4f6f098ce42e69a5f786ef767563e74267e3f9"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-ppeok-capture.wav",
      "text": "싼 패로군. 잘 가져가겠네.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 177960,
      "sha256": "512e1b464bbbe8d78559d423d722bf5e84721192774af7cc009455dcaef38aa1"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-self-ppeok.wav",
      "text": "자뻑이라. 오늘 운이 좋군.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 169898,
      "sha256": "0f3c921052af987963555487fb8a624263f525fcc03914fbb19234f09c19824f"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-score.wav",
      "text": "점수가 났군. 흐름이 좋네.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 178902,
      "sha256": "0eed02f083806cc129f6799f9c4431954633d13009bb15a7fa04df62b37ab43b"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-go.wav",
      "text": "고. 조금 더 가보겠네.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 126672,
      "sha256": "f37b7130a9226084e5cda952c2ffd1df44fcc9bc67ed3a917fc49f99b04b356a"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-stop.wav",
      "text": "스톱. 여기서 마무리하지.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 160686,
      "sha256": "090fb31d07931d9ad37530fc0013c44c3b50c829bec3cb3a1a50fddb90d613fb"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-c-win.wav",
      "text": "내가 이겼군. 좋은 승부였네.",
      "voice": "M5",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 188722,
      "sha256": "e6f80443b719e9d475e87910c204b4f9b2a58409451a4e273266bf7e2f798938"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-capture.wav",
      "text": "어머, 그 패는 제가 가져갈게요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 205794,
      "sha256": "6ec33785a236bb2458a8aa7375ec0c9d3862dedd8c17310cdc58a0c0bedf4dcd"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-bonus-two.wav",
      "text": "쌍피네요. 운도 제 편인가 봐요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 235876,
      "sha256": "582b9335c1b74459acaced387dd095c77dad1713e752eadbfb37e4c8e6559e62"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-bonus-three.wav",
      "text": "쓰리피라니, 꽤 마음에 드네요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 179402,
      "sha256": "8b6287f6f17c51f2910809e58187136adc9050788f9545fe72af03c3026df89c"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-ppeok.wav",
      "text": "어머, 뻑이네요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 89612,
      "sha256": "66ec785377e4857d58aff57716c031f2764436c4cae3ab1be5c4548cbbd0d01c"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-sweep.wav",
      "text": "싹쓸이네요. 전부 제 거예요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 204578,
      "sha256": "47944138a395196f6eed5d4c2e174e6f53f08fb5089e13efee04d369e4d23506"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-ppeok-capture.wav",
      "text": "싼 패네요. 제가 챙길게요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 208052,
      "sha256": "9deea50e687a866391cfbc13cd46b77064e9359d0944a749a2c09f938a0fbed7"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-self-ppeok.wav",
      "text": "자뻑이라니, 운이 따라주네요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 177000,
      "sha256": "59aae2bba6382ba327f9d60e84985eb50949e61a015928b704b3feaec0b55578"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-score.wav",
      "text": "점수가 났네요. 흐름이 좋은데요?",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.98,
      "bytes": 228174,
      "sha256": "a9dea135f9eb38ee9aeb4c1ed2983900e7f3c837c723cb132eb2e03b40066da2"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-go.wav",
      "text": "고. 조금 더 즐겨볼까요?",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 172934,
      "sha256": "fbeee98d4c86cdd603861184727ff506b287d5f89cccc16a0371c0079292f1bf"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-stop.wav",
      "text": "스톱. 여기서 끝낼게요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 164908,
      "sha256": "b05feddb9fb640c5e0e3c004e914c4b27c3d4f5283bd69660fafcece4f0b5277"
    },
    {
      "file": "gostop-computer-d-win.wav",
      "text": "제가 이겼네요. 즐거운 승부였어요.",
      "voice": "F3",
      "speed": 0.96,
      "bytes": 252072,
      "sha256": "eeec696cf3ec472c4feac5b835fd89ddac049eea28bebd705dc935dc3233ed01"
    }
  ]
}
